Class RDKitAdapterCell

    public class RDKitAdapterCell
extends AdapterCell
implements RDKitMolValue
    An RDKit Adapter Cell combines multiple chemical molecule value representations in one cell.

    Thorsten Meinl, University of Konstanz, Manuel Schwarze, Novartis

                        AdapterValue copy)
        Creates a new adapter cell and adds the passed in cell and copies all cells that are contained in the passed in copy parameter.
        Parameters:
        copy - An existing adapter value, from which all cells are copied into the new adapter cell. Can be null.
        cell - Cell to be added to the existing cell collection. Must not be null.
